Package com.coveros.selenified.utilities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constants
    Constants simply holds constant variables to be used through out the application for checks
    Hub
    Utilities class to interact with some remote hub driver, retrieving information such as username, key, and test status
    LambdaTest
    Utilities class to interact with lambda test, retrieving information such as username, key, and test status
    Listener
    Appends additional test links and information into the TestNG report file, for easier tracking and viewing of detailed custom test reports.
    Property
    Reads in properties files provided by the user in order to execute tests.
    Reporter
    A custom output file, recording all details of every step performed, both actions and app.
    ReportOverview
    Creates a custom report at the conclusion of the test run, which nicely lays out the high level results, and links to all of the detailed reports
    Sauce
    Utilities class to interact with sauce labs, retrieving information such as username, key, and test status
    TestCase
    Manages the test cases, including naming conventions and formatting
    Transformer
    Programmatically sets an invocation count for each test, based on the number of browsers desired to test on.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Reporter.Success
    Determines if the tests pass or fail
